        public PayRefundParamChain builderOutRequestNo(String outRequestNo)

      • builderOrgPid

        public PayRefundParamChain builderOrgPid(String orgPid)
        It Is Useful In The Bank To Bank Mode. Please Do Not Use It In Other Scenarios; Through This Parameter, The Double Link Specifies The PID Of The Acquirer Of The Exchange To Be Refunded;

        银行间联模式下有用,其它场景请不要使用: 双联通过该参数指定需要退款的交易所属收单机构的PID;

        Parameters:
        orgPid - orgPid
        Returns:
        PayRefundParamChain
